race.description: Warrnambool Toyota Charge @ Beersheba Sprint Hcp
race.comment: SPEIR (3) went fast early and went on to score by 2.2L first-up over 1000m at Moe, jumping a $2.0 favourite. Drawn to go forward again and has a handy 3kg claim. The promising galloper can go back-to-back. FORAGOODCAUSE (9) has been busting to win and tumbles in weight in this contest. That brings him right into it and under Yendall will finish hard. DEMOJO (1) didn't have the best of it seeking the hat trick in stronger at Cranbourne. He will push forward and rates to be fighting out the finish. BALLYNACALLY (8) resumes and has won both jumpouts. Placed her only fresh outing and her best form stacks up. Should be further improved and Linda stays aboard. BINE (5) is threatening a win and was only beaten 2L at Caulfield Heath last time. In the mix.
